#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:63
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The idea behind &kappname; is simple, but addictive. Each of two possible "
#| "players controls a satellite spaceship orbiting the sun. As the game "
#| "progresses players have to eliminate opponent's spacecraft. As soon as "
#| "the opponent's satellite is destroyed, the remaining player wins the "
#| "round."
msgid ""
"The idea behind &kspaceduel; is simple, but addictive. Each of two possible "
"players controls a satellite spaceship orbiting the sun. As the game "
"progresses players have to eliminate opponent's spacecraft. As soon as the "
"opponent's satellite is destroyed, the remaining player wins the round."
msgstr ""
"Ideja koja stoji iza &kappname; je jednostavna, ali zarazna. Svaki od dva "
"moguća igrača kontrolira svemirski brod satelit u orbiti oko Sunca. Kako "
"igra napreduje igrači moraju eliminirati protivnički svemirski brod. Čim "
"protivnički satelit je uništen, preostali igrač osvaja krug."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to Play"
msgstr "Kako igrati"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "Objective:"
msgstr "Cilj:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "Destroy the opponent's satellite, while keeping the own one in tact."
msgstr "Uništiti protivnikov satelit, uz zadržavanje vlastitog netaknutim."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:70
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kappname; loads directly into the game mode; however, the action does "
#| "not start until either player makes the first move."
msgid ""
"&kspaceduel; loads directly into the game mode; however, the action does not "
"start until either player makes the first move."
msgstr ""
"&kappname; učitava se direktnu u režim igre; Međutim, akcija ne počinje sve "
"dok oba igrača ne naprave prvi potez."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the opponent's satellite is controlled by the built in artificial "
"intelligence, game action does not start until the human player makes the "
"first move."
msgstr ""
"Ako se protivnički satelit kontrolira putem ugrađene umjetne inteligencije, "
"igra ne počinje dok  ljudski igrač ne uradi prvi potez."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:73
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "In &kappname; you control the ship's rotation, acceleration, and "
#| "weaponry. Your satellite is constantly drawn towards the sun by gravity. "
#| "You have to adjust the rotation and acceleration of your ship to make it "
#| "stay on course."
msgid ""
"In &kspaceduel; you control the ship's rotation, acceleration, and weaponry. "
"Your satellite is constantly drawn towards the sun by gravity. You have to "
"adjust the rotation and acceleration of your ship to make it stay on course."
msgstr ""
"U &kappname; kontrolirate rotacije broda, ubrzanje, i naoružanja. Vaš "
"satelit se konstantno vuče prema suncu zbog gravitacije. Morate podesiti "
"rotaciju i ubrzanje svog broda kako bi ga ostao na kursu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid "Approaching the sun too close causes the satellite to explode."
msgstr "Približavanje preblizu sunce uzrokuje satelit da eksplodira."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the same time you have to monitor the opponent's movement and use your "
"weapons consisting of bullets and mines, to destroy the enemy spacecraft."
msgstr ""
"U isto vrijeme morate pratiti kretanje protivnika i koristiti oružje koje se "
"sastoji od metaka i mina, da uništite neprijateljski svemirski brod."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Your own weapons are as harmful to your satellite as they are to the enemy "
"one."
msgstr "Tvoj oružja su štetne za tvoj satelit, koliko su i za neprijateljski."

