#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:119
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "About Energy Points."
msgid "About Energy Points"
msgstr "Energetski bodovi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "Each player controls one ship."
msgstr "Svaki igrač kontroliše jedan brod."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid "The ships can rotate, accelerate, shoot and set mines."
msgstr "Brodovi mogu rotirati, ubrzavati, pucati i postavljati mine."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each ship has a limited amount of energy required for rotation, "
"acceleration, shooting and setting mines."
msgstr ""
"Svaki brod ima ograničenu količinu energije koja je potrebna za rotaciju, "
"ubrzanje, pucanje i postavljanje mina."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid "Each ship has a limited amount of energy."
msgstr "Svaki brod ima ograničenu količinu energije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Ships absorb solar energy required for the ship's operation. The amount of "
"energy the ship gets depends on the distance from and the direction to the "
"sun."
msgstr ""
"Brodovi upijaju sunčevu energije potrebnu za rad na brodu. Iznos energije "
"koju brod dobija ovisi o udaljenosti od i pravcau u odnosu na sunce."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A ship gets more energy near the sun and less energy near the border. It "
"gets the full amount of energy if the sun shines directly on the solar "
"panels and less or even no energy if the sun shines at an angle to the "
"panels or at the other side of the panels."
msgstr ""
"Brod dobija više energije u blizini sunca i manje energije u blizini "
"granice. Postaje puni iznos energije, ako sunce sija direktno na solarne "
"panele, a manje ili čak bez energije ako sunce sija pod uglom na ploče ili "
"na drugoj strani ploče."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:130
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "About Bullets and Mines."
msgid "About Bullets and Mines"
msgstr "O metcima i minama."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bullets fly around the sun just like a ship does."
msgstr "Metci lete oko Sunca baš kao što brod radi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Mines have an amount of energy to stay at the same position. When the energy "
"is spent, the mines collide with the sun and disintegrate."
msgstr ""
"Mine imaju količinu energije dovoljnu da ostanu na istoj poziciji. Kad se "
"potroši energija, mine se sudaraju sa suncem i raspadaju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The closer to the sun the mine is set, the more energy it needs to stay in "
"place."
msgstr ""
"Što je bliže suncu mina postavljena, više energije je potrebno da ostane na "
"mjestu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mines can be destroyed with bullets."
msgstr "Mine mogu biti uništene sa metcima."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid "By default each ship has 5 bullets and 3 mines."
msgstr "Podrazumijevano svaki broj ima 5 metaka i 3 mine."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid "About Hit Points"
msgstr "O bodovima pogodaka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Collision with own bullets, or enemy bullets or mines decreases the hit "
"points."
msgstr ""
"Sudar sa vlastitim metcima, ili neprijateljskim metacima ili minama smanjuje "
"bodove pogodaka."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If two ships collide then the weaker ship is destroyed and the hit points of "
"the stronger ship are decreased by the amount of the hit points the weaker "
"ship had."
msgstr ""
"Ako se dva broda sudare onda je slabiji brod uništen i bodovi pogodaka jačeg "
"broda se smanjuju za iznos bodova koje je slabiji brod imao."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:144
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If the satellite's amount of hit points goes to zero then satellite "
#| "explodes."
msgid "If the ship's amount of hit points goes to zero then ship explodes."
msgstr ""
"Ako iznos satelitovih bodova pogodaka ode onda na nulu satelit eksplodira."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:145
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If a satellite collides with the sun it is destroyed regardless of the "
#| "amount of hit points remaining."
msgid ""
"If a ship collides with the sun it is destroyed regardless of the amount of "
"hit points remaining."
msgstr ""
"Ako se satelit sudari sa suncem, uništen je bez obzira na iznos njegovih "
"bodova pogodaka."

